Datasets that Can be used : 
CelebA — CelebFaces Attributes Dataset (real faces)
(https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/jessicali9530/celeba-dataset)
Large dataset of real celebrity faces.

AI-GENERATED (Fake) Dataset:
CIFAKE — Real vs AI Generated Synthetic Images
(https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/philosopher0808/real-vs-ai-generated-faces-dataset)
Useful for AI_GENERATED class training.

Deepfake-style dataset (usable as AI-edited examples):
Real and Fake Face Detection Dataset (Kaggle)
(https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ciplab/real-and-fake-face-detection)
Contains face images including photoshopped/fake images that can be used as AI-edited examples in project.

